#: _versions/3.33/guides/grpc-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you need to implement a gRPC service or consume it, you need the `quarkus-grpc` extension.\n"
"It handles both sides."
msgstr "如果您需要实现 gRPC 服务或调用该服务，则需要使用 `quarkus-grpc` 扩展。该扩展可同时处理这两种情况。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/grpc-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using Maven"
msgstr "使用 Maven"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/grpc-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To enable gRPC, add the following dependency to your project:"
msgstr "要启用 gRPC，请将以下依赖项添加到您的项目中："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/grpc-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus:generate-code` goal is executed by default during the Quarkus Maven plugin default lifecycle when using the `quarkus` packaging,\n"
